definitions.definition: Clipping of natural ( “ pertaining to a dice roll before bonuses or penalties have been applied to the result ” ) .
examples: After rolling a Strength check to move a heavy cabinet, I got a nat 1 and the cabinet fell on me.

main_definition: ( roleplaying games , dice games , slang ) Clipping of natural ( “ pertaining to a dice roll before bonuses or penalties have been applied to the result ” ) .
